des: This is an illustration of using Doctor Andy's Fuzzy logic rule based system to create skills. This takes a set of rules that come from a well-known article By Karen Hao in the MIT review, and automates them. You can use the rules to determine if an example application, for instance Alexa, uses AI or not. Just answer the questions about the application
